-comman.jpg" alt="">--> <!--</div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/iic.jpg" alt="">--> <!--</div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/in-mou.jpg" alt="">--> <!--</div>--> <div class="the-slide"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/placements.jpg" alt=""> </div> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/team-sistec.jpg" alt="">--> <!--</div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/winner.jpg" alt="">--> <!--</div>--> <!-- <div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-00000.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- <div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-0001.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- <div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-19.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- <div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-102.jpg" alt="Slide 102">--> <!--</div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-103.jpg" alt="Slide 103">--> <!--</div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-104.jpg" alt="Slide 104">--> <!--</div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-105.jpg" alt="Slide 105">--> <!--</div>--> <!-- <div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-222.jpg" alt="Slide 222">--> <!--</div>--> <!-- <div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-223.jpg" alt="Slide 223">--> <!--</div>--