 <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-12.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- </div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-13.jpg" alt="">--> <!--</div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-14.jpg" alt="">--> <!--</div>--> <!--<div class="the-slide">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-sliders/home-slider-15.jpg" alt="">--> <!--</div>--> </div> </section> <section> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <div class="accreditation-logos-container"> <div> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/25-years.png" alt=""> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/naac.png" alt=""> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/nba-1.png" alt=""> </div> <div class="space-y-5"> <div> <h2 class="logos-strip-title">Centres of Excellence</h2> <div class="coe-logos-strip"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/coe/eicher.png" class="eicher"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/coe/ultratech.png" class="ultratech"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/industry/renault.png" class="renault"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/coe/netlink.png" class="netlink"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/gaia.jpg" class="gaia"> </div> </div> <div> <h2 class="logos-strip-title long-line">Industry Partners</h2> <div class="coe-logos-strip"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/industry/cisco.png" class="cisco"> <!--<img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/industry/l-t.png" class="lnt">--> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/coe/bosch.png" class="bosch"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/accreditation/coe/aws.png"> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section id="the-sgi"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-6"> <h1 class="this-title underline-dash center text-center primary-clr" data-aos="fade-down"> Sagar Group of Institutions </h1> <div class="web-text-paras" data-aos="fade-up"> <p> Sagar Group of Institutions which was established in the year 2007 under the aegis of Shri Agrawal Educational & Welfare Society with the main objective of imparting quality education. </p> <p> Sagar Group of Institutions have emerged as a group of Best Private Colleges in Bhopal with its state-of-the-art facility and its expertise in Engineering, Pharmacy, and MBA education. Three institutional campuses rich in infrastructure and amenities proudly flourish under the aegis of the brand Sagar Group of Institutions. </p> <p> The brand has a strong motivation towards innovation in curriculum implementation with its unique industry-oriented pedagogy. It further aspires to be a part of an educational revolution in technical education, impacting advanced futuristic technologies in the national and international framework, and aims to be one of the finest providers of technical education in India. </p> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-6"> <section id="home-video"> <div> <video autoplay loop muted playsinline> <source src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/videos/CV-1-first teaser.mp4"> </video> </div> <!-- <div class="d-block d-md-none"> <video autoplay loop muted playsinline> <source src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/videos/sistec-video-mobile.mp4"> </video> </div> --> </section> </div> </div> </div> </section> <!----> <!-- <section id="students-speak">--> <!-- <div class="container">--> <!-- <div class="row">--> <!-- <div class="col-md-12">--> <!-- <h1 class="this-title underline-dash center text-center primary-clr" data-aos="fade-down">--> <!-- Spotlight--> <!-- </h1>--> <!-- <div data-aos="fade-up">--> <!-- <div class="spotlight-slider">--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/event/sagar-exuberance-2024">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-126460884.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Sagar Exuberance 3.0--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.facebook.com/sagargroupofinstitutionssistec/posts/pfbid037njKEexqpJpJ1cPGR57U3KP8jVrV9kqkqMQRizoUrWArobFTFM3tEPhpnqZnnphQl">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-707069796.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- AI Innovation Hackathon - Samadhan 1.0--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/event/tedx-sistec-bhopal-rethinking-education-quality-by-design">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-617594782.JPG" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- TEDx SISTec 2024 Rethinking Education - Quality by Design--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/MRyfy33Tqebx9FQ1/">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-265526006.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Inauguration of CoE in Advanced Automotive Engineering powered by Renault Nissan --> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://sistec.ac.in/event/sagar-glory-2024-celebrations-of-magnificent-placements">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-578984035.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Sagar Glory 24--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://sistec.ac.in/award-recognition-accolades">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-407761206.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Navdunia Jyotirmaya Award 2024--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://sistec.ac.in/award-recognition-accolades">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-390908303.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Team Velocity won Cash Prize at Lakecity Hack--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://sistec.ac.in/award-recognition-accolades">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-161600938.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Jagran Josh Education Award 2024--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://sistec.ac.in/event/nirmaan-2024-national-level-tech-skill-expo-xii-edition">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-693502670.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Nirmaan 2024 Tech-Skill Expo--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://sistec.ac.in/event/sistec-innovation-hackathon-2024">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-766374275.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- SISTec Innovation Hackathon 2.0--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/event/celebrity-night-at-sistec-live-performance">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-632624745.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Celebrity Night 2024--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/event/prerana-igniting-professional-minds">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-488226727.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Inaugural of IoT Centre of Excellence--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/mou-industry-collaboration">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-758054431.jpeg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- MoU with University of Cape Coast, Ghana--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/mou-industry-collaboration">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-717108096.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- MoU with Perdana University Malaysia--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/event/inaugural-of-ultr-tech-centre-of-excellence">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-792889551.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Inaugural of UltraTech Centre of Excellence in Sustainable Construction Materials--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- <a class="spotlight-card" href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/event/prerana-igniting-professional-minds">--> <!-- <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/home-spotlights/home-spotlight-805207199.jpg" alt="">--> <!-- <p>--> <!-- Session by Former, Vice Chairman of AICTE, Dr. M.P Poonia--> <!-- </p>--> <!-- </a>--> <!-- --> <!-- </div>--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- </section>--> <!----> <section id="home-courses"> <div class="home-courses-card"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-8"> <div data-aos="fade-right"> <h1 class="text-white ff-semibold big-title"> Engineering </h1> <div class="web-text-paras"> <p class="text-white"> The B.Tech. Engineering Program at Sagar Group of Institutions is developed from an industrial point of view, with a great focus on modern technologies employed in the industries. Engineers are the focal point in our economy to design, test, and develop the next generation of products and services for the betterment of society. In this regard, the pedagogy is designed based on industry-oriented training modules a level extra than the standard university curriculum. Similarly, the MTech Engineering Program is developed from a research point of view to inculcate the spirit of innovation and development in Science & Technology. </p> </div> </div> <div class="course-content-row"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-6"> <div class="the-courses" data-aos="fade-down"> <h2 class="course-name">B.Tech.</h2> <div class="course-content"> <div class="course-text"> <ul class="web-list-style no-padding distance li-white"> <li>Civil Engineering</li> <li>Computer Science & Engineering</li> <li>Computer Science & Information Technology</li> <li>CSE with Artificial Intelligence and Data Science</li> <li>CSE with Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning</li> <li>CSE with Internet of Things</li> <li>CSE with Cyber Security</li> <li>Electrical & Electronics Engineering</li> <li>Electrical Engineering</li> <li>Electronics & Communication Engineering</li> <li>Mechanical Engineering</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-6"> <div class=" the-courses mt-mob" data-aos="fade-up"> <h2 class="course-name">M.Tech.</h2> <div class="course-content"> <div class="course-text"> <ul class="web-list-style no-padding distance li-white no-justify"> <li>Computer Science & Engineering</li> <li>Construction Technology and Management</li> <li>Digital Communication</li> <li>Machine Design</li> <li>Power System</li> <li>Structural Engineering</li> <li>Thermal Power & Engineering</li> <li>Very Large Scale Integration (VLSI) Design</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-4"> <div class="course-video right"> <div> <div class="shape-div"> <div class="video-div" data-aos="fade-left"> <video muted loop autoplay playsinline class="shape-video" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="600"> <source src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/videos/engg.mp4"> </video> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="home-courses-card"> <div class="container"> <div class="row mob-flex-direction-col-reverse"> <div class="col-md-4"> <div class="course-video left"> <div> <div class="shape-div"> <div class="video-div right-bg" data-aos="fade-right"> <video muted loop autoplay playsinline class="shape-video" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="600"> <source src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/videos/pharm.mp4"> </video> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-8"> <div data-aos="fade-left"> <h1 class="text-white ff-semibold big-title"> Pharmacy </h1> <div class="web-text-paras"> <p class="text-white"> <!-- The B.Pharm., M.Pharm., and D.Pharm. Programs at Sagar Group of Institutions has undergone significant reform to introduce more clinical pharmacy aspects as compared to the traditional aspect. A lot of focus is given to the practical aspect of pharmacy with a maximum time of students invested in the laboratories. The end goal for the pharmacy program is designed to enhance the public healthcare system by enabling the students to practice the pharmacy profession in a strong, skillful, and determined manner. Interaction with community pharmacists and industrial experts is constant with ample support from the faculty members. --> The B.Pharm. and M.Pharm. Programs at Sagar Group of Institutions has undergone significant reform to introduce more clinical pharmacy aspects as compared to the traditional aspect. A lot of focus is given to the practical aspect of pharmacy with a maximum time of students invested in the laboratories. The end goal for the pharmacy program is designed to enhance the public healthcare system by enabling the students to practice the pharmacy profession in a strong, skillful, and determined manner. Interaction with community pharmacists and industrial experts is constant with ample support from the faculty members. </p> </div> </div> <div class="course-content-row"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-4"> <div class="the-courses" data-aos="fade-down"> <h2 class="course-name">B.Pharm.</h2> <div class="course-content"> <div class="course-text"> <ul class="web-list-style no-padding distance li-white"> <li>Bachelor of Pharmacy</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-4"> <div class=" the-courses mt-mob" data-aos="fade-up"> <h2 class="course-name">M.Pharm.</h2> <div class="course-content"> <div class="course-text"> <ul class="web-list-style no-padding distance li-white"> <li>Pharmaceutics</li> <li>Pharmaceutical Chemistry</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!--<div class="col-md-4">--> <!-- <div class="the-courses" data-aos="fade-down">--> <!-- <h2 class="course-name">D.Pharm.</h2>--> <!-- <div class="course-content">--> <!-- <div class="course-text">--> <!-- <ul class="web-list-style no-padding distance li-white">--> <!-- <li>Diploma in Pharmacy (Applied)</li>--> <!-- </ul>--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- </div>--> <!-- </div>--> <!--</div>--> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="home-courses-card"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-8"> <div data-aos="fade-right"> <h1 class="text-white ff-semibold big-title"> Management </h1> <div class="web-text-paras"> <p class="text-white"> The Management Programs at Sagar Group of Institutions are the flagship programs designed to be a career-building experience for students, developing them into socially responsible and highly skilled managers, master in leading their organization towards excellence. The pedagogy is designed such that students gain exposure to theory and practice alike. The programs include theoretical lectures, audio-visual lectures, case studies, paid/unpaid internships, learning by events & activities, and lab-based learning. Students receive a foundational level of management education with a great focus on the key management disciplines, subjects, and issues. </p> </div> </div> <div class="course-content-row"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-6"> <div class="the-courses" data-aos="fade-down"> <h2 class="course-name">MBA</h2> <div class="course-content"> <div class="course-text"> <ul class="web-list-style no-padding distance li-white"> <li>Master of Business Administration</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <!-- <div class=" the-courses mt-mob" data-aos="fade-up"> <h2 class="course-name">Specializations</h2> <div class="course-content"> <div class="course-text"> <ul class="web-list-style no-padding distance li-white"> <li>Financial Management</li> <li>Marketing Management</li> <li>Human Resource Management</li> <li>Retail Management</li> <li>Banking and Financial Services Management</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> --> </div> <div class="col-md-6"> <div class=" the-courses mt-mob" data-aos="fade-up"> <h2 class="course-name">BBA</h2> <div class="course-content"> <div class="course-text"> <ul class="web-list-style no-padding distance li-white"> <li>Bachelor of Business Administration</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-4"> <div class="course-video right"> <div> <div class="shape-div"> <div class="video-div" data-aos="fade-left"> <video muted loop autoplay playsinline class="shape-video" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="600"> <source src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/videos/management.mp4"> </video> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section id="web-counter" class="mt-0"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <h1 class="this-title underline-dash center text-center text-white" data-aos="fade-down"> The SIST<span class="text-lowercase">ec</span> Spread </h1> </div> <div class="col-md-3"> <div class="counter-card" data-aos="fade-up"> <div> <div class="counter-icon"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/counter/years-in-education.png" alt=""> </div> </div> <div class="counter-content"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count ff-semibold" counter-lim="25">25</span> <span class="plus-sign">+</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Years in Education </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-3"> <div class="counter-card mt-mob" data-aos="fade-down"> <div> <div class="counter-icon"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/counter/skilled-faculties.png" alt=""> </div> </div> <div class="counter-content"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count ff-semibold" counter-lim="2000">2000</span> <span class="plus-sign">+</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Highly Skilled Faculties </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-3"> <div class="counter-card mt-mob" data-aos="fade-up"> <div> <div class="counter-icon"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/counter/network.png" alt=""> </div> </div> <div class="counter-content"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count ff-semibold" counter-lim="25000">25000</span> <span class="plus-sign">+</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Students Network </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-3"> <div class="counter-card mt-mob" data-aos="fade-down"> <div> <div class="counter-icon"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/counter/jobs.png" alt=""> </div> </div> <div class="counter-content"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count ff-semibold" counter-lim="1150">1150</span> <span class="plus-sign">+</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Job Offers to 2025 Batch </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section id="coe"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <h1 class="this-title underline-dash center text-center primary-clr" data-aos="fade-down"> Centres of Excellence </h1> </div> </div> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <div class="new-coe-card-grid"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/eicher-centre-excellence-farm-machinery"> <div class="new-coe-card"> <div class="title-area"> <p> CoE in Farm Machinery <br> In association with <span class="tertiary-clr">Eicher Tractors</span> </p> </div> <div class="image-area"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/eicher.jpg" alt=""> </div> </div> </a> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/ultratech-centre-of-excellence"> <div class="new-coe-card"> <div class="title-area"> <p> CoE in Sustainable Construction Material <br> In association with <span class="tertiary-clr">UltraTech Cement</span> </p> </div> <div class="image-area"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/ultratech.jpg" alt=""> </div> </div> </a> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/iot-centre-of-excellence"> <div class="new-coe-card"> <div class="title-area"> <p> CoE in IoT and Measurement Science supported by <span class="tertiary-clr">Gaia Smart Cities</span> </p> </div> <div class="image-area"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/gaia.jpg" alt=""> </div> </div> </a> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/centre-of-excellence-advance-automotive-engineering"> <div class="new-coe-card"> <div class="title-area"> <p> CoE in Advance Automotive Engineering <br> In association with <span class="tertiary-clr">Renault Nissan Tech</span> </p> </div> <div class="image-area"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/renault-nissan.jpg" alt=""> </div> </div> </a> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/centre-of-excellence-data-analytics"> <div class="new-coe-card"> <div class="title-area"> <p> CoE in Data Analytics <br> Supported by <span class="tertiary-clr">Netlink</span> </p> </div> <div class="image-area"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/netlink-lumenore.jpg" alt=""> </div> </div> </a> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/semiconductor-technology-centre-of-excellence"> <div class="new-coe-card"> <div class="title-area"> <p> CoE in Semiconductor Technology <br> Supported by <span class="tertiary-clr">AICTE and MeitY </span> </p> </div> <div class="image-area"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/semiconductor-technology.jpg" alt=""> </div> </div> </a> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/automotive-skills-development-centre-of-excellence"> <div class="new-coe-card"> <div class="title-area"> <p> CoE in Soft Skills and Automotive Skills Development <br> Supported by <span class="tertiary-clr">BOSCH BRIDGE </span> </p> </div> <div class="image-area"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/bosch-bridge.jpg" alt=""> </div> </div> </a> </div> </div> <!-- <div class="col-md-3"> <div class="coe-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/eicher-centre-excellence-farm-machinery"> <div class="title"> <p title="CoE in Farm Machinery in association with Eicher Tractors">CoE in Farm Machinery in association with Eicher Tractors</p> </div> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/eicher.jpg" alt=""> </a> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-3"> <div class="coe-card mt-5 mt-md-0"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/ultratech-centre-of-excellence"> <div class="title"> <p title="CoE in Sustainable Construction Material in association with UltraTech Cement">CoE in Sustainable Construction Material in association with UltraTech Cement</p> </div> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/ultratech.jpg" alt=""> </a> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-3"> <div class="coe-card mt-5 mt-md-0"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/iot-centre-of-excellence"> <div class="title"> <p title="CoE in Internet of Thing">CoE in Internet of Things</p> </div> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/iot.jpg" alt=""> </a> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-3"> <div class="coe-card mt-5 mt-md-0"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/iot-centre-of-excellence"> <div class="title"> <p title="CoE in Advance Automotive Engineering in association with Renault Nissan Tech"> CoE in Advance Automotive Engineering in association with Renault Nissan Tech</p> </div> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/coe/Centre-of-Excellence-Renault-Nissan-Website-Update.jpg" alt=""> </a> </div> </div> --> </div> </div> </section> <section id="flip-cards"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <h1 class="this-title underline-dash center text-center primary-clr" data-aos="fade-down"> The Making of a Refined Professional </h1> </div> </div> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <div class="flip-box-container" data-aos="fade-up"> <div class="box-item"> <div class="flip-box"> <div class="flip-box-front flip-box-div text-center"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/home/flip-box/F1.jpg" alt=""> <div class="inner"> <h3 class="flip-box-header text-uppercase ff-semibold"> Academic <br> Excellence </h3> </div> </div> <div class="flip-box-back flip-box-div"> <div class="inner"> <ul> <li>Project Oriented Training</li> <li>Outcome Based Education</li> <li>Blended Teaching Learning</li> <li>Value Based Education</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="box-item mt-mob"> <div class="flip-box"> <div class="flip-box-front flip-box-div text-center"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/home/flip-box/F2.jpg" alt=""> <div class="inner"> <h3 class="flip-box-header text-uppercase ff-semibold"> 360&deg; <br> Training </h3> </div> </div> <div class="flip-box-back flip-box-div text-center"> <div class="inner"> <ul> <li>Placement Oriented Training</li> <li>Industry Approved Training Content</li> <li>Exclusive Training APP for Students</li> <li>Training Validation on National Platforms</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="box-item mt-mob"> <div class="flip-box"> <div class="flip-box-front flip-box-div text-center"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/home/flip-box/F3.jpg" alt=""> <div class="inner"> <h3 class="flip-box-header text-uppercase ff-semibold"> Student <br> Grooming </h3> </div> </div> <div class="flip-box-back flip-box-div text-center"> <div class="inner"> <ul> <li>Tech-Talks</li> <li>Industrial Visits</li> <li>Student Clubs</li> <li>Professional Chapters</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="box-item mt-mob"> <div class="flip-box"> <div class="flip-box-front flip-box-div text-center"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/home/flip-box/F4.jpg" alt=""> <div class="inner"> <h3 class="flip-box-header text-uppercase ff-semibold"> Magnificent <br> Placements </h3> </div> </div> <div class="flip-box-back flip-box-div text-center"> <div class="inner"> <ul> <li>22 LPA by BNY Mellon</li> <li>96% Campus Placements</li> <li>1150+ Job Offers for 2024-25 Batch</li> <li>15 Startups</li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section> <div id="counter-section" data-aos="fade-up"> <div class="counter-grid"> <div class="counter-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/placements/counter/job-offer.png" class="count-icon"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count" counter-lim="1150">1150</span> <span class="plus-sign">+</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Job Offers for 2024-25 Batch </div> </div> <div class="counter-div two"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/placements/counter/cash-on-delivery.png" class="count-icon"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count" counter-lim="4.8">4.8</span> <span class="plus-sign">LPA</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Average Package </div> </div> <div class="counter-div three"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/placements/counter/package.png" class="count-icon"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count" counter-lim="22">22</span> <span class="plus-sign">LPA</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Highest Package By BNY Mellon </div> </div> <div class="counter-div four"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/placements/counter/internship.png" class="count-icon"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count" counter-lim="100">100</span> <span class="plus-sign">%</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Internships </div> </div> <div class="counter-div five"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/placements/counter/mou.png" class="count-icon"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count" counter-lim="30">30</span> <span class="plus-sign">+</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> MoUs </div> </div> <div class="counter-div six"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/placements/counter/opportunities.png" class="count-icon"> <div class="count-number"> <span class="count" counter-lim="200">200</span> <span class="plus-sign">+</span> </div> <div class="counter-title"> Campus Opportunities </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section id="placements"> <div class="placement-div"> <div class="upper"> <div class="floating-div"> <div data-aos="fade-left"> <h2 class="text-white text-uppercase ff-semibold">Campus Drives</h2> <div class="placement-slider"> <div class="placement-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/drives-images/EWAC.jpeg"> </div> </div> <div class="placement-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/drives-images/Mastek.jpeg"> </div> </div> <div class="placement-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/drives-images/Pine_Kalpraj_Creative_27Nov2025.jpg"> </div> </div> <div class="placement-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/drives-images/Hexaware_BPS_24thNov2025.jpg"> </div> </div> <div class="placement-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/drives-images/SMPL_Creative_21stNov2025.jpg"> </div> </div> <div class="placement-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/drives-images/Tesla_Transformers_12thNov2025.jpg"> </div> </div> <div class="placement-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/drives-images/Makemytrip.jpeg"> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="first"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <div data-aos="fade-right" class="title"> <p> <span class="ff-semibold">The</span> <span class="ff-semibold big-text">Placement</span> </p> <p class="ff-semibold big-text underline-me">Bulletin</p> </div> <div class="package-div"> <div data-aos="zoom-in"> <p class="ff-semibold me-big">4.8 LPA</p> <p class="me-small">Average Offered Package</p> </div> <div data-aos="zoom-in"> <p class="ff-semibold me-big">22 LPA</p> <p class="me-small">Highest Offered Package</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="second"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <p class="ff-semibold" data-aos="fade-down"> Total offers rolled out for <span class="me-big">2025 </span> batch : <span class="me-big">1150+</span> </p> <p class="ff-semibold" data-aos="fade-up"> Opportunities : 200+ (Batch 2025 ) | Internship : 100% (Batch 2025 ) </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="third d-none d-md-block"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <p class="ff-semibold text" data-aos="fade-right"> <span style="opacity: 0;"> B.Tech - 576 | Pharmacy - 19 | MBA - 56 </span> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="lower"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <div data-aos="fade-up"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/placements/logo-strip.jpg"> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section id="recent-happenings"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <h1 class="this-title underline-dash center text-center primary-clr" data-aos="fade-down"> Recent Happenings </h1> <div class="rh-grid"> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/ai-foundation-application-tcs-vipin-mahajan-01-2026.JPG" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 24 Apr, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/ai-foundation-application-tcs-vipin-mahajan-01-2026.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> AI Foundation & Application: Industry Insight by TCS Expert </p> </a> </div> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/sistec-world-creativity-innovation-day-1.JPG" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 21 Apr, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/sistec-world-creativity-innovation-day-1.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> World Creativity & Innovation Day Celebration </p> </a> </div> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/ultratech-advanced-construction-materials-vac-2026-01.jpg" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 17 Apr, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/ultratech-advanced-construction-materials-vac-2026-01.jpg" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> UltraTech workshop on Advanced Construction Materials & Solutions VAC </p> </a> </div> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/technology-commercialization-1.jpg" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 16 Apr, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/technology-commercialization-1.jpg" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> Expert Session on Technology Commercialization, Licensing and Transfer Practices & Strategy </p> </a> </div> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-sagar-fiesta-2026.JPG" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 02 Apr, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-sagar-fiesta-2026.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> 19th Sagar Fiesta 2026 - ROOTS TO RISE </p> </a> </div> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-mba-headstart.JPG" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 30 Mar, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-mba-headstart.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> SISTec Business School hosted Headstart: The Industry-Academia Forum </p> </a> </div> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-aids-ieee-club-reformation.JPG" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 24 Mar, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-aids-ieee-club-reformation.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> Club Reformation Ceremony of the IEEE Student Branch & CIS Student Chapter </p> </a> </div> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-pre-placement-talk-2026-tcs.JPG" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 17 Mar, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-pre-placement-talk-2026-tcs.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> Pre-Placement Talk for Batch 2026 in collaboration with Tata Consultancy Services </p> </a> </div> <div class="rh-grid-card"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-national-science-day-celebration-2026.JPG" target="_blank"> <p class="date"> 10 Mar, 2026 </p> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/1-national-science-day-celebration-2026.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> <p class="title"> National Science Day Celebration at SIPTec </p> </a> </div> </div> <div class="text-center mt-4"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/events-and-gallery" class="web-btn-one spacing-top"> <span>View More</span> <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> <!-- <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <h1 class="this-title underline-dash center text-center primary-clr" data-aos="fade-down"> Recent Happenings </h1> <div data-aos="fade-up"> <div class="rh-slider-for"> <div class="text-div"> <div class="the-date"> <p class="ff-semibold"> 24-04-2026 </p> </div> <p> AI Foundation & Application: Industry Insight by TCS Expert </p> </div> <div class="text-div"> <div class="the-date"> <p class="ff-semibold"> 21-04-2026 </p> </div> <p> World Creativity & Innovation Day Celebration </p> </div> <div class="text-div"> <div class="the-date"> <p class="ff-semibold"> 17-04-2026 </p> </div> <p> UltraTech workshop on Advanced Construction Materials & Solutions VAC </p> </div> <div class="text-div"> <div class="the-date"> <p class="ff-semibold"> 16-04-2026 </p> </div> <p> Expert Session on Technology Commercialization, Licensing and Transfer Practices & Strategy </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-12"> <div data-aos="fade-up"> <div class="rh-slider-nav center-mode-slick-slider"> <div> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/event/ai-foundation-application-tcs-vipin-mahajan-sistec-ratibad-april-2026" target="_self"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/ai-foundation-application-tcs-vipin-mahajan-01-2026.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> </a> </div> <div> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/event/sistec-world-creativity-innovation-day" target="_self"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/sistec-world-creativity-innovation-day-1.JPG" class="img-mt-spacing"> </a> </div> <div> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/event/ultratech-advanced-construction-materials-vac-sistec-ratibad-17-march-2026" target="_self"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/ultratech-advanced-construction-materials-vac-2026-01.jpg" class="img-mt-spacing"> </a> </div> <div> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/event/-expert-session-on-technology-commercialization-licensing-and-transfer-practices-strategy" target="_self"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/events-images/technology-commercialization-1.jpg" class="img-mt-spacing"> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> --> </section> <section id="virtual-tour"> <div class="vt-video"> <video autoplay muted loop> <source src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/videos/virtual-tour-bg.mp4"> </video> <div class="content"> <div data-aos="fade-down"> <h1 class="text"> Explore <br> <span>Sagar Group of Institutions</span> </h1> <div class="img360"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/home/360-icon.gif" alt="360degree" class="d-block m-auto"> </div> </div> <div class="btns-div" data-aos="fade-up"> <a href="#!" class="web-btn-two effect w-min-300" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#vt-modal-sistec-gn"> <span>SISTec Gandhi Nagar Campus</span> </a> <a href="#!" class="web-btn-two effect w-min-300" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#vt-modal-sistec-rb"> <span>SISTec Ratibad Campus</span> </a> </div> </div> </div> </section> <section id="students-speak"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-12"> <h1 class="this-title underline-dash center text-center primary-clr" data-aos="fade-down"> Stakeholders Speak </h1> <div data-aos="fade-up"> <div class="testimonials-grid"> <a data-fancybox="video-gallery" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WGUnEm5kqEU" class="video-box"> <div class="position-relative"> <img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/WGUnEm5kqEU/maxresdefault.jpg" class="block object-cover object-left-middle w-full"> <div class="play-div"> <i class="fas fa-play"></i> </div> </div> <div class="text-div"> <p> Ms. Lata Tekam <br> CSE Batch 2025 | Placement Byte </p> </div> </a> <a data-fancybox="video-gallery" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jYegrq0BAIc" class="video-box"> <div class="position-relative"> <img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jYegrq0BAIc/maxresdefault.jpg" class="block object-cover object-left-middle w-full"> <div class="play-div"> <i class="fas fa-play"></i> </div> </div> <div class="text-div"> <p> Mr. Amul Chandravanshi <br> ME Batch 2025 | Placement Byte </p> </div> </a> <a data-fancybox="video-gallery" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RAUxJTObfgE" class="video-box"> <div class="position-relative"> <img src="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/RAUxJTObfgE/maxresdefault.jpg" class="block object-cover object-left-middle w-full"> <div class="play-div"> <i class="fas fa-play"></i> </div> </div> <div class="text-div"> <p> Prathmesh Borikar <br> Computer Science & Engineering Batch 2024 </p> </div> </a> </div> <div class="text-center mt-4"> <a href="https://sistec.ac.in/video-gallery" class="web-btn-one spacing-top"> <span>View More</span> <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> </a> </div> </div> <!-- <div data-aos="fade-up"> <div class="student-speak-slider center-mode-slick-slider"> <div class="testimonial-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/testimonials/dimpy-kumari.jpg"> </div> <div class="text-center name-div"> <h2 class="ff-semibold text-uppercase">Dimpy Kumari</h2> <p class="tc-text"> Electrical and Electronics Engineering <br> (Batch 2016-20) </p> </div> <div class="text-center comment-div"> <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <p class="tc-text"> SISTec provided me with great knowledge, and confidence, and helped develop my body language. The credit for my good career goes to all my faculties and placement cell. </p> </div> </div> <div class="testimonial-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/testimonials/priti-kumari.jpg"> </div> <div class="text-center name-div"> <h2 class="ff-semibold text-uppercase">Priti Kumari</h2> <p class="tc-text"> Computer Science & Engineering <br> (Batch 2018-22) </p> </div> <div class="text-center comment-div"> <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <p class="tc-text"> I had big dreams for my engineering journey and I worked on new technologies and developed skills with each semester. SISTec is the place where I got a platform to hone my skills. </p> </div> </div> <div class="testimonial-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/testimonials/ritik-shrivastava.jpg"> </div> <div class="text-center name-div"> <h2 class="ff-semibold text-uppercase">Ritik Shrivastava</h2> <p class="tc-text"> Computer Science & Engineering <br> (Batch 2018-22) </p> </div> <div class="text-center comment-div"> <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <p class="tc-text"> College is not just about studies, it's a combo of studies, co-curricular, and cultural activities. I would like to thank SISTec for providing me with exceptional support during my college journey. </p> </div> </div> <div class="testimonial-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/testimonials/manas-nair.jpg"> </div> <div class="text-center name-div"> <h2 class="ff-semibold text-uppercase">Manas Nair</h2> <p class="tc-text"> Mechanical Engineering <br> (Batch 2018-22) </p> </div> <div class="text-center comment-div"> <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <p class="tc-text"> The college has helped me in grooming my personality and given me opportunities to show my leadership and presentations skills, I'm thankful to SISTec for numerous platforms. </p> </div> </div> <div class="testimonial-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/testimonials/bhavana-raghuwanshi.jpg"> </div> <div class="text-center name-div"> <h2 class="ff-semibold text-uppercase">Bhavana Raghuwanshi</h2> <p class="tc-text"> Axis Bank <br> HR Operations Senior Executive </p> </div> <div class="text-center comment-div"> <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <p class="tc-text"> We had an interesting session with the SISTec students and looking forward to having some good candidates for our company, you were a really good host to us. </p> </div> </div> <div class="testimonial-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/testimonials/surya-tiwari.jpg"> </div> <div class="text-center name-div"> <h2 class="ff-semibold text-uppercase">Surya Tiwari</h2> <p class="tc-text"> Airtel <br> Manager B2B </p> </div> <div class="text-center comment-div"> <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <p class="tc-text"> It was a nice opportunity to have a campus in SISTec Bhopal, we have got a good quality refined student which we were actually looking for. Thank you SISTec for cooperating with us. </p> </div> </div> <div class="testimonial-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/testimonials/tanuj-soni.jpg"> </div> <div class="text-center name-div"> <h2 class="ff-semibold text-uppercase">Tanuj Soni</h2> <p class="tc-text"> Edelweiss Tokio <br> Marketing Manager </p> </div> <div class="text-center comment-div"> <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <p class="tc-text"> We got a good pool of students from SISTec, the facilities provided were very great, big thanks to the volunteers and the staff for overall support. Would surely come back. </p> </div> </div> <div class="testimonial-card"> <div class="img-div"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/testimonials/pankaj-kumar-malik.jpg"> </div> <div class="text-center name-div"> <h2 class="ff-semibold text-uppercase">Pankaj Kumar Malik</h2> <p class="tc-text"> IndusInd Bank <br> Training & HR Dept. </p> </div> <div class="text-center comment-div"> <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> <p class="tc-text"> I found SISTec to be a good group, with good infra. I took a presentation and hope to get good candidates for my organization. Hopeful for a future association too. </p> </div> </div> </div> --> </div> </div> </div> </div> </section> </section> <!-- Modal --> <div class="modal fade" id="admissionModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="admissionModal" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="home-modal-slider"> <div class="home-modal-slider-div"> <div class="modal-header"> <h5 class="modal-title"> <div class="home-modal-slider-for"> <div> <a href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/admissions"> <h1 class="text-white"> <strong>Admissions Open 2026</strong> </h1> </a> </div> </div> </h5> <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button> </div> <div class="modal-body"> <div class="home-modal-slider-nav"> <div> <a href="https://www.sistec.ac.in/admissions"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/upload/modal/modal-341862501.jpg" title="Admissions Open 2026" class="home-page-modal-img" /> </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div><script src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script> <footer class="footer overflow-hidden"> <div class="footer-content"> <div class="container"> <div class="row"> <div class="col-md-5"> <div data-aos="fade-down"> <img src="https://sistec.ac.in/assets/web/images/footer/bottom-logo-2025.png" class="golden-years w-100 mb-3"> <div class=""> <h1 class="title"> Sagar Institute of Science and Technology&reg; </h1> <ul class="web-list-style white hover no-justify dist